==French==
===Etymology===
Compound of ''[[au]]'' and ''[[jour]]'' and ''d''' (see ''[[de]]'') and ''[[hui]]'', litterally "in the day of today"

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ɔ.ʒuʁ.dɥi/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /O.ZuR.dHi/

===Adverb===
'''aujourd'hui'''

# [[today]]

===See also===
